Document: VisualShaderNodeParticleRandomness
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodeparticlerandomness.rst
Summary: The op_type property and its setter/getter methods for controlling operand types in VisualShaderNodeParticleRandomness.

OpType op_type = 0
- void set_op_type(value: OpType)
- OpType get_op_type()

A type of operands and returned value. The OpType enum defines valid options for this property, with 0 as the default value. The setter method allows changing the operand type, while the getter retrieves the current value. This property determines how the node processes particle randomness data in visual shaders.